<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٧١٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5093">أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2149">زِيَادِ بْنِ عِلَاقَةَ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1133">جَرِيرًا </a><span class="special">﵁</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«بَايَعْتُ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>،<span class="c5"> فَاشْتَرَطَ عَلَيَّ:</span> وَالنُّصْحِ لِكُلِّ مُسْلِمٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>